# AI_Cue Agent Harness

This project follows harness engineering. At the start of every session, before responding to any user request, you MUST:

1. Read `Agent.md` in the project root
2. Read `TODO.md` to check current project progress

`Agent.md` contains:
- Project context and tech stack reference
- Mandatory workflow (e.g. propose solution before coding)
- Code style and communication rules
- Document conventions

Follow its instructions throughout the session. When human engineers update `Agent.md` after agent errors, subsequent sessions will inherit the improved constraints.

You must NEVER modify `TODO.md`. Only human engineers may edit it.

`TODO.md` progress markers (set by human engineers only):
- ✅ = task completed
- ❌ = task not completed
